  ]

const TournamentFormComponent = () => {

    const [percentCoopAgent, setPercentCoop] = React.useState(0)
    const [percentDefectAgent, setPercentDefect] = React.useState(0)
    const [percentCopyAgent, setPercentCopy] = React.useState(0)
    const [percentGrudgeAgent, setPercentGrudge] = React.useState(0)
    const [percentAIAgent, setPercentAI] = React.useState(0)
    const onChange = (event) => {
        switch(event.target.id) {
            case 'coop':
                setPercentCoop(event.target.value)
                break
            case 'defect':
                setPercentDefect(event.target.value)
                break
        }
    }
    const onSubmit = (event) => {
        console.log(event)
    }

    return <Form onSubmit = {onSubmit}>
        <Form.Group widths='equal'>
            <Form.Field
                label = 'Percent Cooperate Agent'
                id = 'coop'
                control = 'input'
                type = 'number'
                max = {100}
                min  = {0}
                onChange = {onChange}
            />
            <Form.Field
                label = 'Percent Defect Agent'
                id = 'defect'
                control = 'input'
                type = 'number'
                max = {100}
                min  = {0}
            />            
            <Form.Field
                label = 'Percent Copy Agent'
                id = 'copy'
                control = 'input'
                type = 'number'
                max = {100}
                min  = {0}
                onChange = {onChange}
            />
            <Form.Field
                label = 'Percent Grudge Agent'
                id ='grudge'
                control = 'input'
                type = 'number'
                max = {100}
                min  = {0}
                onChange = {onChange}
            />
            <Form.Field
                label = 'Percent AI Agent'
                id = 'ai'
                control = 'input'
                type = 'number'
                max = {100}
                min  = {0}
                onChange = {onChange}
            />
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group>
            <Form.Field
                label = 'Generations'
                id = 'genenerations'
                type = 'number'
                onChange = {onChange}
            />
            <Form.Field
                label = 'Interactions'
                id = 'interactions'
                type = 'number'
                onChange = {onChange}
            />
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Button type='submit'>Load Tournament Visual</Form.Button>
    </Form>

}

export default TournamentFormComponent;
